# .gitignore for an Xcode macOS Swift project
# 忽略 Xcode 构建产物、用户配置、SwiftPM/CocoaPods 缓存以及大文件样本

### macOS
.DS_Store
.AppleDouble
.LSOverride

### Xcode
# Build / derived
build/
DerivedData/

# User-specific settings
xcuserdata/
*.xcuserdatad
*.xcuserstate

# Workspace user data
*.xcworkspace/xcuserdata/

# Scheme / workspace generated files
*.xcscmblueprint
*.xccheckout

# Misc Xcode artifacts
*.moved-aside
*.hmap
*.ipa
*.xcarchive
*.dSYM
*.app
*.framework
*.xcframework

### Swift Package Manager
.build/
Packages/
.swiftpm/
# Package.resolved is usually committed for apps; uncomment to ignore
# Package.resolved

### CocoaPods
Pods/

### Carthage
Carthage/Build/

### fastlane
fastlane/report.xml
fastlane/Preview.html
fastlane/screenshots

### IDEs / Editors
.idea/
.vscode/
*.swp
*~
*.sublime-project
*.sublime-workspace

### Common generated / temporary
*.lock
*.log
*.tmp

### Large data / example files (ignore anywhere in repo)
**/alldata.csv
**/alldata.gpx
**/exampledata/

# Optional: ignore local environment files
.env
.env.local

# Node / frontend (if present)
node_modules/
",